  "note": [
    {
      "text": "Diagnosed at 28 weeks gestation in third pregnancy. Abnormal 100 g 3-hour glucose tolerance test with 3 of 4 values abnormal. A1c 5.3% excludes pregestational diabetes. Initial management with diet, exercise, and home glucose monitoring."
    },
    {
      "text": "Resolved postpartum. Six-week postpartum follow-up on 2022-06-10 confirmed normal fasting glucose (88 mg/dL) and A1c (5.4%), consistent with complete metabolic normalization after delivery. Patient counseled on elevated lifetime type 2 diabetes risk and recommended annual screening."
    }
  ],
